{"tid":1308640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 東區禮義廉星期日想搞東區遊行   呼籲街坊參加","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T13:03:23.000Z","uid":211021,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9baa6e3f6d6db83675a4ae05e0fdff8ffd9936","tid":1308640,"uid":211021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"東區民賤聯話要搞東區遊行呼籲街坊參加 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日期： 14/7 (星期日） <br />\n集合時間： 10:am <br />\n集合地點： 愛東邨愛東廣場 <br />\n<br />\n歡迎港島人起身10點去東區 <br />\n聲援支持興建筲箕灣新泳池 並且表達社區民意<br />\n<br />\n大家一定都要爭取屋企樓下都有泳池！<br />\n筲箕灣要有自己泳池 點解 鰂魚涌 北角 砲台山 銅鑼灣唔可以有自己嘅泳池？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 大家千祈唔好騎劫個遊行 </span></span><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反送中都係民意之一呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 大家記得去完呢個，就好去沙田喇 </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4ZYcoc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4ZYcoc.jpg&h=b78277f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhBr5Je.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhBr5Je.jpg&h=522ad513&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31fb96dff7fcbb9a40aa6827d3c98ed858f8abb5","tid":1308640,"uid":276216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci